# Agra Local Guide - Context File

## City Overview
Agra is a historic city in Uttar Pradesh, India, famous for the Taj Mahal.

## Local Food Culture
- **Petha**: Panchhi Petha, Bhimsain Devidayal
- **Breakfast**: Bedai-Jalebi at Deviram Sweets
- **Street Food**: Dalmoth, Chaat at Sadar Bazaar

## Local Slang
- "Bhaiya/Didi" - Brother/Sister
- "Thoda adjust karo" - Please adjust
- "Chalega" - It will work

## Tourist Tips
- Visit Taj at sunrise (6-7 AM)
- Mehtab Bagh for sunset view
- Bargain at Sadar Bazaar

